<typeStatus box="[151,249,1365,1391]" pageId="8" pageNumber="239">syntypes</typeStatus>
were found at 
<collectionCode box="[427,488,1365,1391]" country="Germany" httpUri="http://grbio.org/cool/8syf-d21i" name="Museum für Naturkunde Berlin (Zoological Collections)" pageId="8" pageNumber="239" type="Museum">ZMB</collectionCode>
